The paper discusses the challenges and factors impacting the driveability of autonomous vehicles, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for autonomous driving, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the need for datasets for training and testing autonomous driving systems, which could fall under systems and control (cs.SY).
